lines.text: Jeff and I are leavin' this pack. We don't like travelin' with mongrels.
[Instead of stealing the stagecoach's strongbox as they planned, Sunset and Jeff defeat a rival gang's robbery attempt - an act witnessed by the sheriff's daughter]
Oh, Jeff, I almost forgot to tell you - her father is the sheriff.
You don't say? Now that makes everything just dandy.
Oh, you must know him. He's quite famous!
Oh, he must be one we missed.
Oh, we just dote on sheriffs.
